Meta shifted to no ignite going top, maybe people need to pick some characters with global ultimates and take ignite and just crap on him early game or change their way of thinking about teleport and he'll go away (or at the very least be dealt with that round). 

Teleport being mandatory top is not at all true, you just have to think of other ways to make plays. Power pushing and invading the enemy jungle early game with ignite is incredibly powerful, as well as roaming mid.

